{"tid":1186523,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"冰凍3萬年！西伯利亞穴獅幼屍出土　保存完整就像活著","createTime":"2019-06-05T03:41:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-05T04:07:23.000Z","uid":32511,"like":17,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"4559767ee25e923241dace7959430d0043157542","tid":1186523,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-05T03:41:47.000Z","msg":"自然充滿驚奇，不時有讓人讚嘆的發現，有機會讓世界更多人窺探世界奧秘。俄羅斯與日本的聯合研究團隊於前（3）天對外公布，從西伯利亞的永凍土發現呈冰凍狀態的穴獅幼獅及狼的頭部，因為寒帶地區氣溫極低，降低細菌存活率，不少生物死後容易成為凍屍。據了解，這兩者均是距今約3萬年冰河時期的個體，且能夠分辨表情，保存狀態被稱為「奇蹟般良好」！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2019/06/05/1958038-XXL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2019%2F06%2F05%2F1958038-XXL.jpg&h=5d7d321e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2019/06/05/1958037-XXL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2019%2F06%2F05%2F1958037-XXL.jpg&h=2fe9ad6f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n▲日、俄聯合研究團隊公布，於西伯利亞發現距今3萬年的穴獅乾屍。<br />\n<br />\n根據研究團隊公布的內容提到，東京慈惠會醫科大學與俄羅斯科學院的科學家，去年7月到西伯利亞研究時，在東北部河川附近發現一隻長約40公分、體重約800克，研判為剛出生不久的穴獅雌性幼獅遺體，被命名「斯巴達克」（Spartak）。讓科學家大感驚奇的是，斯巴達克的肌肉、內臟及腦部等皆被良好保存，讓古生物學教授鈴木直樹又驚又喜地說「看起來就像還活著！」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2019/06/05/1958039-XXL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2019%2F06%2F05%2F1958039-XXL.jpg&h=c6d87e71&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲因穴獅乾屍出土保存完整，讓科學家驚喜「看起來就像活著」！<br />\n<br />\n俄羅斯科學院動物博物館館長帝霍諾夫（Tikhonov）表示，未來研究人員將繼續研究這兩隻動物的身體組織和DNA，以利於了解古生物生態，以及與現代同類生物的關係；並希望能更透過基因，有朝一日將這些美麗的生物複製出來。"},{"pid":"6ce55b4df465b5a6ad3ab72560a79a01bdfbe24b","tid":1186523,"uid":148332,"like":25,"dislike":0,"score":25,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-05T03:43:53.000Z","msg":"點解唔帶口罩,一陣污染到個標本點算<br />\n利申:唔識,門外漢求解答"},{"pid":"ee1e00fdf67a1c6788f862a46b9ecad1a23a6316","tid":1186523,"uid":65346,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-05T03:46:24.000Z","msg":"D 國家開始收集古生物 DNA , 小心"},{"pid":"449a44e45368674834f82b2a669cc53f265291bd","tid":1186523,"uid":130105,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"ee1e00fdf67a1c6788f862a46b9ecad1a23a6316","tid":1186523,"uid":65346,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-05T03:46:24.000Z","msg":"D 國家開始收集古生物 DNA , 小心"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-05T03:53:17.000Z","msg":"一路做緊複制研究，五年內就有長毛象，你未聽過咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5cf081c669d74cd83d1cea6a2472d8ae6a0df671","tid":1186523,"uid":73340,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-05T03:55:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n隻幼獅極速冰凍先會保存得咁完整<br />\n氣候異常？"},{"pid":"2974a3ba085dae40aea3a083ceba673bd59b7f35","tid":1186523,"uid":76705,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-05T03:57:09.000Z","msg":"Biohazard<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/27.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01aabcafc4ed6501220bb59cbc94cffc6df6535f","tid":1186523,"uid":239435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-05T03:58:22.000Z","msg":"好得意"},{"pid":"65f6bd72d0097bf9ef46d7019a343a8d6283bb89","tid":1186523,"uid":33907,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-05T03:59:05.000Z","msg":"冰人四萬年<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bac996fe9635a51bcc90132fbe2c3310db153cc6","tid":1186523,"uid":49016,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-05T03:59:35.000Z","msg":"最後果張好劇照feel"},{"pid":"2e92b32a9d4da823726b16ecf473b577d6d67fb0","tid":1186523,"uid":120070,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-05T04:00:05.000Z","msg":"Jurassic Park 2.0"},{"pid":"1747109bc3bd5f69026f10edda224d8781affac8","tid":1186523,"uid":147376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"449a44e45368674834f82b2a669cc53f26529